<br>
If an untwinked monk and shaman entered my guild (which isn't going to happen as it's level restricted .. but barring that) at such a low level, I'd give each 50p to work with, and I'm sure a guild could help you do well on Sullon Zek as well (Having friends would be nice in pvp I assume).<br>
<br>
Additionally, the guild might have a Dark Elf Wizard to port its members around.  While 20 platinum isn't enough to get anything better than maybe two pieces of Wu's or maybe a Polished Steel Ulak, wizards can port you directly to the Nexus, which is adjacent to the Bazaar. <p>-Korph
